Check out this music video for God is an Astronaut's "Spiral Code" sent in by KSPC listeners and this week's featured artists Tyler Haywood and Johnny Chew!

"Our inspiration for the video revolved around a few elements, but we were really drawn to the psychological theory of Spiral Dynamics which is about Progression and Regression of Human Development. Our visuals consisted of a free form collage of 3D elements, heavy texturing, and found footage. We wanted to tell an openly interpreted story with thematic issues of memory, struggle, and resolution."

-Tyler Haywood

