&nbsp;

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

<strong>The Pharcyde </strong>- These LA legends are still active performers. They haven’t released much aside from remixes and a few singles as of late, so I’m anticipating hearing the classics. It’s hard to turn down a chance to hear “Passing Me By” and “Runnin’” live.

<img class=" wp-image-5814 alignleft" src="/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/a1327378404_5-300x300.jpg" alt="a1327378404_5" width="185" height="185" />

