<strong>Gucci Mane</strong> – Guwop is fresh out and already has two albums out, his latest being the days old <em>Woptober</em>. Gucci has been a preeminent force in rap for 15 years and his influence is heard throughout KSPC’s hip-hop library. Some verses he has done are scattered in the library. I’m unbelievably excited, Gucci is one of my favorite rappers, but also curious as to what he’ll play. I’m assuming plenty of the hits along with a few notable tracks from his latest projects.

<img class=" wp-image-5816 alignleft" src="/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Grimes_-_Art_Angels.png" alt="grimes_-_art_angels" width="185" height="185" />

